<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-20">
  <div class="text-center mb-16">
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">Help Center</h1>
    <p class="text-xl text-gray-400">Frequently Asked Questions & Support</p>
  </div>

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <div class="glass-card p-10 rounded-3xl mb-12">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-8 text-primary">Common Questions</h2>

    <div class="space-y-6">
      <details
        class="group bg-black/20 rounded-xl p-4 transition-all hover:bg-black/30"
      >
        <summary
          class="flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer font-bold text-lg"
        >
          How do I verify my profile?
          <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180">▼</span>
        </summary>
        <div
          class="text-gray-400 mt-3 pl-4 border-l-2 border-primary/30 leading-relaxed"
        >
          Go to your Profile > Settings > Verification. You can verify via phone
          number or connect your social accounts for a blue tick.
        </div>
      </details>

      <details
        class="group bg-black/20 rounded-xl p-4 transition-all hover:bg-black/30"
      >
        <summary
          class="flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer font-bold text-lg"
        >
          Is Interesta free?
          <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180">▼</span>
        </summary>
        <div
          class="text-gray-400 mt-3 pl-4 border-l-2 border-primary/30 leading-relaxed"
        >
          Yes! You can join, create a profile, discover people, and chat for
          free. We offer premium features like "Unlimited Swipes" and "Travel
          Mode" for power users.
        </div>
      </details>

      <details
        class="group bg-black/20 rounded-xl p-4 transition-all hover:bg-black/30"
      >
        <summary
          class="flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer font-bold text-lg"
        >
          How does the referral system work?
          <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180">▼</span>
        </summary>
        <div
          class="text-gray-400 mt-3 pl-4 border-l-2 border-primary/30 leading-relaxed"
        >
          When you invite a friend using your unique code, both of you get 1
          week of Premium features for free! There's no limit to how many
          friends you can invite.
        </div>
      </details>

      <details
        class="group bg-black/20 rounded-xl p-4 transition-all hover:bg-black/30"
      >
        <summary
          class="flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer font-bold text-lg"
        >
          How do I delete my account?
          <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180">▼</span>
        </summary>
        <div
          class="text-gray-400 mt-3 pl-4 border-l-2 border-primary/30 leading-relaxed"
        >
          We'd hate to see you go! But if you must, go to Settings > Account >
          Delete Account. This action is permanent.
        </div>
      </details>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Contact Form -->
  <div class="glass-card p-10 rounded-3xl text-center">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Still have questions?</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-400 mb-8">
      Our support team is available 24/7 to assist you.
    </p>

    <form class="max-w-md mx-auto space-y-4">
      <input
        type="email"
        placeholder="Your Email"
        class="w-full bg-black/40 border border-white/10 rounded-lg px-4 py-3 text-white placeholder-gray-500 focus:outline-none focus:border-primary transition"
      />
      <textarea
        rows="4"
        placeholder="How can we help?"
        class="w-full bg-black/40 border border-white/10 rounded-lg px-4 py-3 text-white placeholder-gray-500 focus:outline-none focus:border-primary transition"
      ></textarea>
      <button
        type="submit"
        class="w-full bg-primary hover:bg-primary-dark text-white font-bold py-3 rounded-lg transition"
      >
        Send Message
      </button>
    </form>
  </div>
</div>
